letion messages are just stale notifications from earlier build attempts—the actual build passed successfully. So while the session status changed, the underlying work is complete, and the HEARTBEAT_OK message suggests the agent already processed this as a non-event.\n\nSince the DTLX ecosystem session ended and that's a legitimate state change, I should update the heartbeat file to reflect this new status and report it to the QLHV group.","thinkingSignature":"3460a7cd6143c7edff7dfa7328b5c9789fb6d136db277badf098ffc1ef935c02"},{"type":"text","text":"Now comparing current state against the stored heartbeat state to detect changes.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_764qgxsxnwdd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastChecked\": \"2026-04-15T02:56:00Z\",\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"cron:6f3323ef\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"DTLX 5p Monitor\", \"startedAt\": \"2026-04-14T20:44:00Z\", \"note\": \"running ~6h 12m — persistent long-running monitor\" },\n    \"cron:ed2d0b5d\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"5p QLHV monitor\", \"startedAt\": \"2026-04-15T02:03:00Z\", \"note\": \"active cycle — current session\" },\n    \"cron:e7885813\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Agent Status to Lead\", \"note\": \"Cycle completed 02:44 UTC, new cycle restarted normally\" },\n    \"cron:ac986a8d\": { \"status\": \"orphaned\", \"label\": \"Telegram send cron\", \"startedAt\": \"2026-04-14T13:04:00Z\", \"note\": \"⚠️ ORPHANED — ~23.8h stale. Needs kill.\" },\n    \"cron:53c5832a\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7\", \"note\": \"completed normally ~23:16 UTC Apr 14 — expected\" },\n    \"main\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"note\": \"running — triggered this 5p report\" },\n    \"telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"ENDED normally 02:37 UTC Apr 15 — session completed\" },\n    \"telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"note\": 